    modified_response: "I\'ve restored the full Stomach Oriental website and beautifully woven the cinematic features\342\200\224like the full-screen dynamic backdrop, the sleek liquid glass navbar overlays, and staggered typographic fade-ups\342\200\224directly into the restaurant\'s aesthetic.\n\nHere is what was finalized:\n- **Cinematic Landing Stage**: Your hero section now functions as the requested immersive viewport with the custom liquid glass buttons and the bottom blur mask to smoothly guide viewers down the page. \n- **Restored \"The Cravings\" & \"Legacy\" Modules**: As viewers scroll past the cinematic fold, the landing page organically reveals your original menu grids (`Classic Steamed Momos`, `Triple Schezwan Rice`), the jogeshwari street heritage story section, and the interactive sumo sanctuary map.\n- **Brand Typography Reinstituted**: Integrated the custom **Space Grotesk** and **Syne** typography paired alongside the sophisticated dark theme and crimson-red glow mechanics from the earliest design iterations."
